      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative equivalency of simulation and experimental input parameters confirmed.",
      "rationale": "Fluid properties, rotational speed, and flow rate in simulation match experimental conditions within measurement uncertainty. Formal equivalency quantification not required at MRL 2. Qualitative review confirms no systematic offset between simulation and experimental input parameters."
    }
